# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../ai.rst:25
msgid ""
"OpenShot can connect to a local `ComfyUI <https://github.com/comfyanonymous/"
"ComfyUI>`_ server and run AI workflows from the Project Files and Timeline "
"context menus. This page explains what these tools are, what hardware they "
"require, and where the built-in workflow templates live."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot dapat terhubung ke server `ComfyUI <https://github.com/"
"comfyanonymous/ComfyUI>`_ lokal dan menjalankan alur kerja AI dari menu "
"konteks File Proyek dan Timeline. Halaman ini menjelaskan apa saja alat-alat "
"tersebut, perangkat keras apa yang diperlukan, dan di mana templat alur "
"kerja bawaan berada."

